snippet.title: CompliKATed trailer
snippet.description:
CompliKATed is a scrolling tile-based puzzle game with logic gates mechanics. 
Features
 -brain twisting logic gates puzzles
- witty gravity objects
- alternative play-styles: swiftly find your escape or strategically plan your path
- ramping progression that will put even the most resilient to test
classic and new mechanics fluently intertwined
- 19 functional tiles: signal generators, sensor, timer, directional tiles, etc
- controller support
- 8 bit retro style sound
- smooth and balanced controls
